1. dialog is useful for quick GUI configuration. 
2. pythondialog is a wrapper around dialog. it is faster to develop
3. install pythondialog on aarch64 processor as the following. (ubuntu16.04LTS)
    1) sudo apt install python3-pip; pip3 install --upgrade pip
    2) sudo pip3 install pythondialog
4) install dialog on aarch64 processor
    sudo apt install dialog
